summary: DOT CODE RYB4 0MAC 0214 COMMODORE ST225/75R15 (RY = SHANDONG CHANGFENG TYRES CO., LTD., CANNOT FIND IN THE SUBSEQUENT SELECTIONS ON THIS SITE) TREAD SEPARATION, NOTICED WHEN WE GOT HOME AND I WAS SECURING THE WHEELS. HAD TIRE REPLACED, NOTICED "BUBBLE SEEN ON THE INSIDE OF THE TIRE, ABOUT AS BIG AROUND AS A BASEBALL/SOFTBALL. TIRES WERE ON A 1987 AVION MODEL 34W TRAVEL TRAILER (34', THREE-AXLE)
